- Add `HAMLISCache(LISCacheInterface)` class skeleton.
    - Include detailed comments outlining design considerations for a HAM-based implementation,
      covering data storage, metadata usage for querying, and handling of updates.
      Full implementation of HAMLISCache methods is deferred.

This commit establishes the interface for the IMMUNO-NARRATIVE CACHE and provides
initial design thoughts for its HAM-based persistence, paving the way for
further LIS component development.
